channel.title: Christmas Models Package 2010!
channel.description:
Hello well, I want to wish you all a merry christmas and a happy new year!
This is for Preloaded clients ONLY, also I only have renamed ints since I lost my non-renamed client, if someone is willing to non rename them for me I would be very greatful!
In this package you will get;
A Christmas stocking, and elf hat and a present box to store items!
